To determine the sustainable growth rate, let us first compute the return on equity:
&nbsp;
$$\begin{aligned}
\text{Return on Equity}&=\text{Profit Margin}\times\text{Total Asset Turnover}\\[5pt]
&\times\text{Equity Multiplier}\\[12pt]
&={5.2\%}\times{2.90}\times{1.10}\\[12pt]
&=\boxed{0.1659}\\
\end{aligned}$$
&nbsp;
**The return on equity is 0.1659.**
